840
01:25:19,800 --> 01:25:21,927
lt's time to put this behind us.

841
01:25:22,002 --> 01:25:23,867
lt's gone on too long.

842
01:25:24,304 --> 01:25:25,931
This has to stop.

843
01:25:26,406 --> 01:25:27,737
