844
01:25:27,808 --> 01:25:30,333
Things will take
their natural course, Lindsey.

845
01:25:30,410 --> 01:25:34,972
Len, l appreciate everything you've done.
You've been a great friend to me.

846
01:25:38,618 --> 01:25:40,711
That goes for Abigail, too.

847
01:25:41,421 --> 01:25:44,219
You've been a great friend to both of us.

848
01:26:28,869 --> 01:26:30,894
<i>Murder changes everything.</i>

849
01:26:41,448 --> 01:26:44,747
<i>When l was alive, l never hated anyone.</i>

850
01:26:45,986 --> 01:26:48,955
<i>But now, hate was all that l had.</i>

851
01:26:49,723 --> 01:26:51,315
l want him dead.

852
01:26:52,893 --> 01:26:57,830
l want him cold and dead
with no blood in his veins!

853
01:27:02,903 --> 01:27:04,268
Look at me.

854
01:27:05,906 --> 01:27:07,931
Look at what he did to me!

855
01:27:09,142 --> 01:27:10,700
What am l now?

856
01:27:10,777 --> 01:27:15,214
The dead girl?
The lost girl? The missing girl?

857
01:27:15,949 --> 01:27:17,348
l'm nothing!

858
01:27:49,649 --> 01:27:51,116
l was stupid.

859
01:27:53,753 --> 01:27:55,618
l was so stupid!

860
01:27:55,689 --> 01:27:57,247
You don't control this, Susie.

861
01:28:13,807 --> 01:28:15,570
He does not own you.

862
01:28:17,577 --> 01:28:21,411
You can be free of him, but not this way.

863
01:28:21,481 --> 01:28:24,973
What do you know?
You don't know anything.

864
01:28:25,051 --> 01:28:27,110
