875
01:29:51,037 --> 01:29:52,299
Come out!

876
01:29:53,106 --> 01:29:54,903
Come out and face me!

877
01:29:55,842 --> 01:29:58,367
Did you hear me, you son of a bitch?

878
01:30:03,984 --> 01:30:05,349
Get off me!

879
01:30:06,052 --> 01:30:07,542
You sick fuck!

880
01:30:09,956 --> 01:30:13,119
Brian, stop! Please, stop!

