884
01:30:26,406 --> 01:30:27,498
Dad!

885
01:30:32,112 --> 01:30:33,170
No.

886
01:30:33,246 --> 01:30:34,645
Brian, stop!

887
01:30:38,885 --> 01:30:40,819
Brian, stop! Stop!

888
01:30:42,455 --> 01:30:44,980
Don't you get it? You've killed him!

889
01:30:47,460 --> 01:30:48,552
-He's dead!
-Go.

890
01:30:48,628 --> 01:30:50,528
