891
01:32:19,719 --> 01:32:23,155
<i>l knew then he would never give me up.</i>

892
01:32:24,958 --> 01:32:27,950
<i>He would never count me</i>
<i>as one of the dead.</i>

893
01:32:30,997 --> 01:32:32,726
<i>l was his daughter.</i>

894
01:32:34,467 --> 01:32:36,128
<i>And he was my dad.</i>

895
01:32:37,704 --> 01:32:41,037
