928
01:47:41,106 --> 01:47:42,334
My girl.

929
01:47:43,709 --> 01:47:44,801
Jack.

930
01:48:10,836 --> 01:48:12,235
Look at you.

931
01:48:13,539 --> 01:48:15,029
