950
01:51:04,676 --> 01:51:07,577
l don't know,
but he gives me the skeevies.

951
01:51:07,646 --> 01:51:09,944
The skeevies? What are you, 12?

952
01:53:07,666 --> 01:53:09,190
lt's beautiful.

953
01:53:11,536 --> 01:53:13,527
Of course it's beautiful.

954
01:53:14,906 --> 01:53:16,305
lt's heaven!

955
01:53:39,564 --> 01:53:42,590
All right, come on. Let's go. l got to...

956
01:53:49,141 --> 01:53:51,769
What are you waiting for? You're free!

957
01:53:58,683 --> 01:53:59,877
Almost.

958
01:54:01,720 --> 01:54:03,051
Not quite.

959
01:54:14,232 --> 01:54:15,290
Ray!

960
